# Code Owners for Fiszki Project
# This file defines who should be automatically requested for review
# when files in certain paths are modified in a Pull Request

# Global ownership - all files require review from repository owner
* @bzfs

# Specific ownership for critical areas
/.github/workflows/ @bzfs
/Fiszki.Database/ @bzfs
/Fiszki.Services/ @bzfs
*.csproj @bzfs
*.sln @bzfs

# Documentation
README.md @bzfs
